It should be noted that this strategy could be considered an exploit.  It could also be fixed in a future patch and he will ignore equipment handed to him. <br>
<br>
I prefer to err on the side of caution, given the lack of real guidelines for what constitutes an exploit and what does not, this tactic may result in sanctions against groups/guilds/individuals who attempt it.<br>
<br>
Of course I also think the Bard strategy known as &quot;Twisting&quot; should be considered an exploit, but Verant has stated that this is a valid strategy for bards and do not punish anyone for using it.  Good luck killing Brother Zephyl if that is what you decide to do.<br>
