I have done this fight many ways - everytime the level 60 warrior uses his defensive disc Zephyl seems to find some people he hates more than the warrior.  Everytime the warrior used riposete - no one died because Zephyl was really pissed by the time the first heal was needed.<br>
<br>
One other thing that wasnt mentioned above - get Rune V on the main tank before starting.  Main tank aggros beating on Zephyl - he waits for the Rune V to get used up first before hitting his riposete disc.  As soon as zephyl lands his first hits then tanks hits riposete disc.  This gives the main tank almost 15 seconds of fighting solo before any heals or any others join the fight.  This will keep Zephyl on the tank the whole time.<br>
