Sure. This is the one way I've been able to rationalize twisting. I still don't believe it, but it's nice to pretend <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
