<br>
As for bards...<br>
<br>
Norrath is not a real world, it is a magical world.<br>
<br>
Bards twisting need not be justified any better than monks being able to fall hundreds of feet onto solid rock, swim across molten lava, get bitten by a poisonous snake and then instantaneously fix themselves up ;p<br>
<br>
Consider firstly that the bards are heroes, exceptional people and not your average person who can play an instrument.  Consider that their instruments and their very voices are magical.  And consider the possibility that instead of having a repetoire of nursery rhyme CDs they play hoping it will do some good, that they are BARDS, and adventurers, able to adapt their battle-drumming, and other magical battle rhythms to produce whatever inspirational effect or combination of effects they choose (within the constraints of level and twisting skill).<br>
<br>
Personally I find twisting to be entirely believable and think it adds a great component of skill and concentration to EQ.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showMessageRange?topicID=618.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showMessageRange?topicID=618.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showMessageRange?topicID=618.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showMessageRange?topicID=618.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showMessageRange?topicID=618.topic&start=101&stop=115>6</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=618.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showNextMessage?topicID=618.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=618.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.emailToFriend?topicID=618.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.threadControl?topicID=618.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=618.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replie